In this directory stores configuration items for third-party components

Third-party components used by openQRM :

busybox
-> we will compile our own, busybox binary since 
   we need special features of busybox which are not
   enabled/available on (most) standard linux-distributions

hwsetup
-> for hardware detection during the initrd stage

kudzu-knoppix
-> requried by hwsetup

hwdata-knoppix
-> required by hwsetup

defaultkernel
-> this is the kernel for creating the default boot-image from

